entries.title: AI wrote a bill to regulate AI. Now Rep. Ted Lieu wants Congress to pass it.
entries.description: Rep. Ted Lieu uses ChatGPT to write a bill that would recommend new federal regulations for artificial intelligence.

entries.title: TikTok tries to sell ‘Project Texas’ as it fights for survival in the U.S.
entries.description: TikTok is going on the offensive in Washington, D.C., in a stepped-up effort to counter calls to ban the app in the U.S. over its Chinese ownership.

entries.title: DOJ disrupts major ransomware group
entries.description: The FBI has infiltrated and disrupted a major cybercriminal group that extorted schools, hospitals and critical infrastructure around the world, a law enforcement official told NBC News.
